Title: British Gypsum Thistle one coat plaster 7.5kg
Description: Drying to a smooth, matte finish, this gypsum-based British Gypsum Thistle One Coat plaster offers easy hand application to most internal backgrounds. Made up of gypsum hemihydrate formulated with special additives to control its setting profile, this plaster also incorporates a lightweight aggregate to improve workability and make application easy.
